Project opertaions

1-opening project
 As a User , i can open a new Project, so that Customer can Order Parts/items
  
  - user should fill new project form fields 
     (
      project Name [automatically by the system]
      Project Open Date
      Project Close Date
      Project Status [New by the system] 
      )
  
  - System Should Check Forms fileds to make sure that they r filled correctly
  
  - User should click on save Button to save Form data in the System data base 